{"subject_name":"soil","chapters":[{"chapter_name":"Introduction to soil","topics":[{"topic_name":"1 . basic of soil","topic_html":"<div class=\"col-12 col-md-11 col-lg-9 my-2 mx-auto px-2 pb-5 border content-section rounded-2\" data-el=\"section\"><h3 class=\"p-2 mb-2\" data-el=\"heading\">Soil Basic</h3><h5 class=\"p-2 mb-2\" data-el=\"title\">what is soil ?</h5><ul class=\"ul li-disk ps-4 ps-md-5 py-3\" data-el=\"list-container\"><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"><span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"Soi!\">Soi</span></span>l is the uppermost layer of the Earth's <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"ভূত্বক!\">crust</span></span>, composed of <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"খনিজ, জৈব পদার্থ, বায়ু এবং জল!\">minerals, organic matter, air, and water</span></span></li><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"> It forms from the weathering of rocks and the <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"পচন!\">decomposition</span></span> of plant and animal material</li><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"> Soil provides essential nutrients and a <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"বাসস্থান)। \">habitat</span></span> for plants, making it crucial for agriculture and natural ecosystems</li><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"> Its composition varies widely, influencing its <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"উর্বরতা!\">fertility</span></span> and structure</li><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"> Soil supports <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"বিভিন্ন!\">diverse</span></span> microorganisms and is fundamental for water <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"পরিস্রাবণ!\">filtration</span></span> and carbon storage</li><li data-el=\"list\"> The health of soil impacts food production and environmental quality</li><li data-el=\"list\" class=\"\"> Effective soil management is vital for <span style=\"\" class=\"text-info\"><span data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-title=\"টেকসই!\">sustainable</span></span> development and ecosystem balance</li></ul><div class=\"d-flex flex-column box-bg-2 p-2 gap-1 my-2 mx-auto border rounded-1 media-container\" data-el=\"media-container\"><img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/1000057/pexels-photo-1000057.jpeg?auto=compress&amp;cs=tinysrgb&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=627&amp;w=1200\"></div></div>","topic_id":20}],"chapter_id":26}]}